ATOM: ATOM: Asynchronous Total Order Mechanism for Publish/Subscribe
--------------------------------------------------------------------

To build (using Gradle 8.7):
gradle clean build 

To run Kafka (3.9.1 Zookeeper mode):
kafka_start_stop_status.sh start 

To modify ATOM configurations:
Modify the file ATOM/config/args.txt to set the configurations

To run the Baseline:
run_basline.sh 

To run the ATOM:
run_TO.sh